3
00:00:06,954 --> 00:00:10,431
belonged to the researcher. RAGdoll was built to keep

4
00:00:10,431 --> 00:00:11,204
those receipts.

5
00:00:11,254 --> 00:00:15,375
This is the real RAGdoll terminal, resuming a documented

6
00:00:15,375 --> 00:00:19,495
