10
00:00:28,244 --> 00:00:32,512
RAGdoll turns an ambiguous question into a structured research

11
00:00:32,512 --> 00:00:36,780
brief and an executable search plan. The researcher can

12
00:00:36,780 --> 00:00:41,048
inspect every axis, query family, inclusion rule, and source

13
00:00:41,048 --> 00:00:44,368
before approving discovery. Search never starts silently.

14
00:00:44,418 --> 00:00:48,245
Approved queries run through scholarly source adapters. Results are

15
00:00:48,245 --> 00:00:52,072
deduplicated and ranked with visible score components and reasons.

16
00:00:52,072 --> 00:00:55,899
This run retrieved twenty four candidates, but the human

17
00:00:55,899 --> 00:00:59,726
selected the six papers that entered the evidence workflow.

18
00:00:59,776 --> 00:01:04,069
Paper selection and evidence acquisition are separate approvals. RAGdoll

19
00:01:04,069 --> 00:01:08,361
records the source, retrieval state, evidence level, and page

20
00:01:08,361 --> 00:01:12,654
count. Five papers supplied open full text and one

21
00:01:12,654 --> 00:01:15,516
used an explicitly labeled abstract fallback.

22
00:01:15,566 --> 00:01:19,410
The resulting dossier contains seven checkpointed sections and twenty

23
00:01:19,410 --> 00:01:23,254
five cited claims. It states its evidence boundary instead

24
00:01:23,254 --> 00:01:27,098
of claiming exhaustive coverage or novelty. Every accepted citation

25
00:01:27,098 --> 00:01:30,942
identifier had to be present in the bounded evidence

26
00:01:30,942 --> 00:01:32,650
supplied for that section.

27
00:01:32,700 --> 00:01:36,911
A citation is not decorative. From any claim, the

28
00:01:36,911 --> 00:01:41,122
researcher can inspect the exact indexed passage, paper identifier,

29
00:01:41,122 --> 00:01:45,333
page locator, and evidence level. Unsupported questions fail closed

30
00:01:45,333 --> 00:01:48,608
instead of inviting the model to guess.

31
00:01:48,658 --> 00:01:53,138
Model output crosses Pydantic validation before entering domain logic,

32
00:01:53,138 --> 00:01:57,618
while narrow adapters own retrieval, storage, and permissions. Codex

33
00:01:57,618 --> 00:02:02,099
accelerated repository analysis, implementation, testing, and security review. RAGdoll

34
00:02:02,099 --> 00:02:06,579
also contains a real Responses API adapter configured for

35
00:02:06,579 --> 00:02:11,059
GPT five point six. It is contract tested, not

36
00:02:11,059 --> 00:02:14,046
presented as live in this capture.

37
00:02:14,096 --> 00:02:18,083
The acceptance run indexed three hundred seven page-aware chunks.

38
00:02:18,083 --> 00:02:22,070
A manual passage audit found twenty three of twenty

39
00:02:22,070 --> 00:02:26,057
five claims directly supported, preserving the two failures as

40
